React Callbacks 
----------------

    - Callback is shared data should be child to parent
    - React envents way only achieve this.
    

Example : -

Explanation
------------

    - parent component event is passing child component 
    - child component button is triggred that event.


Parent Component-
-------------------

    function Calculator(){


        const [count,setCount] = useState(0)

        const increaseCount = (data) => {

            setCount(data)
        }


        return <div>

            <h1>{count}</h1>

            <PlusButton 
                count = {count}
                increaseCount = {increaseCount}
            
            />


        </div>
    }




Child Component
----------------

   const PlusButton = ({count, increaseCount}) => {
    
        return(
            <button onClick={() => increaseCount(count + 1)}> + </button>
        )
    };